#: prefs.js:187
msgid "GNOME theming is split across a few independent layers, each with its own setting below. Tap the (?) next to a section for details.\n"
"\n"
"• GTK3 / legacy — older-style apps (Firefox, GIMP, many utilities).\n"
"• GTK4 / libadwaita — Files, Settings, Extensions, Tweaks and newer apps; only follows light/dark automatically, styled via a CSS override.\n"
"• Shell — the top bar and overview, separate from all app windows.\n"
"• Qt5/Qt6 apps — separate settings system entirely; optional support via qt5ct/qt6ct further down."
msgstr ""

